WEBVTT

01:57:50.316 --> 01:57:52.483
-Didn't you agree to let us handle it?
-Sir... good morning.

01:57:52.483 --> 01:57:54.483
-Then why talk like this now?
-Georgekutty...

01:57:54.524 --> 01:57:55.899
Phone tapping isn't possible.

01:57:55.899 --> 01:57:57.399
No one is willing to do it.

01:57:57.608 --> 01:57:58.941
If anything goes wrong,

01:57:58.983 --> 01:58:00.941
they won't just lose their job,
they'll end up in jail as well.
